    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>“当帝国腐朽、规则崩塌时，唯一的问题是：谁将登上王座？”</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><u><i><strong>探索、战斗并争夺王冠</strong></i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >步入一个迷人的、受桌面游戏启发的微缩模型世界。在这里，有充满魅力的小雕像和精美的立体战斗场景。击败强大的统治者，夺取他们的王冠，解锁新英雄、战利品和区域。探索越深入，世界越广阔。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284730/extras/3f0ebbee6c41d85ab846ee8ac812006d.poster.avif?t=1763761271\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284730/extras/3f0ebbee6c41d85ab846ee8ac812006d.webm?t=1763761271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284730/extras/3f0ebbee6c41d85ab846ee8ac812006d.mp4?t=1763761271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><u><i><strong>升级并装备你的领主与英雄</strong></i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择你的领主，召集你的英雄，开辟王国地图上的冒险之路。完成大胆的任务，获取强力战利品，并在各个区域中磨炼技艺，为即将到来的战斗做好准备。每一次胜利都让你更接近最终的王冠之战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284730/extras/6a6a67371f6bb861d9cb949cedfb82f8.poster.avif?t=1763761271\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284730/extras/6a6a67371f6bb861d9cb949cedfb82f8.webm?t=1763761271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284730/extras/6a6a67371f6bb861d9cb949cedfb82f8.mp4?t=1763761271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><u><i><strong>征服诸国，完成挑战，揭开世界的奥秘。</strong></i></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《继任者》是一个程序生成的宇宙，充满了待解锁的挑战、谜团和物品。随着你完成任务与挑战，打败各地统治者，将会有更多内容在未来的冒险中向你开放。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284730/extras/43f4d02cf75a4bf41fb4a53476e701bf.poster.avif?t=1763761271\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284730/extras/43f4d02cf75a4bf41fb4a53476e701bf.webm?t=1763761271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284730/extras/43f4d02cf75a4bf41fb4a53476e701bf.mp4?t=1763761271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><u><i><strong>主动权始终掌握在你手中。</strong></i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《继任者》中，你可以随时暂停，制定策略，并在战斗中施展能力，而游戏其他部分将保持暂停状态。这让战斗变得动感十足、精彩纷呈，同时又保有深度的战术性和策略性。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284730/extras/718a63622021914c324b6da2e8f8a85b.poster.avif?t=1763761271\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284730/extras/718a63622021914c324b6da2e8f8a85b.webm?t=1763761271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284730/extras/718a63622021914c324b6da2e8f8a85b.mp4?t=1763761271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><u><i><strong>异域立体场景，丰富战术选择</strong></i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在多样化的生态区域与敌人对决，每个区域都拥有独特的战术玩法，例如能够投掷的斧头、可燃的草地以及野生动物。占据箭塔，或巧妙布置你的队伍，占据优势，甚至可以将敌人踢下悬崖。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284730/extras/54c8933bbebe966a189f9ec9551b5e42.poster.avif?t=1763761271\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284730/extras/54c8933bbebe966a189f9ec9551b5e42.webm?t=1763761271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284730/extras/54c8933bbebe966a189f9ec9551b5e42.mp4?t=1763761271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><u><i><strong>挑战无法无天的派系与他们的统治者。</strong></i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过程序生成系统设计你的征服之旅，自由选择要面对的统治者，并通过设置不同参数打造属于你的冒险。添加特殊规则（Kicker），刷新玩法。完成挑战后还能解锁更多内容，如新派系、统治者、生物群落、道具和英雄。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
